'''Monsoon Mesa''' was the location of a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] base during the [[Battle of Jabiim|Battle of]] [[Jabiim/Legends|Jabiim]]. It was just south of [[Cobalt Station]]. At the end of the battle, the last Republic forces on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] were evacuated from there.

